      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the \"magical bond\" idea but i'm trying to study for a science exam, not a fantasy novel. can you explain the part about \"spooky action at a distance\" without using metaphors like magic or best friends? i need to understand the actual physical implication of how the measurement of one particle affects the other.",
      "source": "evaluator"
